oth offensive and defensive research in NLP security. Moreover, the integration of symbolic grammar rules into continuous-space optimization opens new avenues for neuro-symbolic AI, offering a principled way to inject linguistic knowledge into black-box models. Potential applications include robustness evaluation of content moderation systems, improving defense mechanisms through red-teaming, and enhancing interpretability by identifying structurally subtle failure modes in classifiers.",
